#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.fmin.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.fmin"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmin.fmin:1 of
msgid "Element-wise minimum of array elements."
msgstr "逐元素比较数组元素的最小值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmin.fmin:3 of
msgid ""
"Compare two tensors and returns a new tensor containing the element-wise "
"minima. If one of the elements being compared is a NaN, then the non-nan "
"element is returned. If both elements are NaNs then the first is "
"returned.  The latter distinction is important for complex NaNs, which "
"are defined as at least one of the real or imaginary parts being a NaN. "
"The net effect is that NaNs are ignored when possible."
msgstr ""
"比较两个张量并返回一个包含逐元素最小值的新张量。如果被比较的元素中有一个"
"是 NaN，则返回非 NaN 元素。如果两个元素都是 NaN，则返回第一个元素。后者的"
"区别对于复数 NaN 来说很重要，复数 NaN 的定义是实部或虚部至少有一个是 NaN"
"。其最终效果是尽可能忽略 NaN。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmin.fmin of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmin.fmin:10
#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmin.fmin:13 of
msgid ""
"The tensors holding the elements to be compared. They must have the same "
"shape."
msgstr "包含要比较元素的张量。它们必须具有相同的形状。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmin.fmin:16 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，它必须具有与输入广播兼容的形状。如果未提供"
"或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmin.fmin:21 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmin.fmin of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmin.fmin:26 of
msgid ""
"**y** -- The minimum of `x1` and `x2`, element-wise.  Returns scalar if "
"both  `x1` and `x2` are scalars."
msgstr ""
"**y** -- `x1` 和 `x2` 的逐元素最小值。如果 `x1` 和 `x2` 都是标量，则返回"
"标量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmin.fmin of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmin.fmin:32 of
msgid ":py:obj:`fmax`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmin.fmin:33 of
msgid "Element-wise maximum of two tensors, ignores NaNs."
msgstr "两个张量的逐元素最大值，忽略 NaN。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmin.fmin:35 of
msgid ":py:obj:`minimum`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmin.fmin:36 of
msgid "Element-wise minimum of two tensors, propagates NaNs."
msgstr "两个张量的逐元素最小值，传播 NaN。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmin.fmin:38 of
msgid ":py:obj:`amin`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmin.fmin:39 of
msgid "The minimum value of a tensor along a given axis, propagates NaNs."
msgstr "沿给定轴的张量最小值，传播 NaN。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmin.fmin:41 of
msgid ":py:obj:`nanmin`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmin.fmin:42 of
msgid "The minimum value of a tensor along a given axis, ignores NaNs."
msgstr "沿给定轴的张量最小值，忽略 NaN。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmin.fmin:44 of
msgid ":py:obj:`maximum`, :py:obj:`amax`, :py:obj:`nanmax`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmin.fmin:47 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmin.fmin:48 of
msgid ""
"The fmin is equivalent to ``mt.where(x1 <= x2, x1, x2)`` when neither x1 "
"nor x2 are NaNs, but it is faster and does proper broadcasting."
msgstr ""
"当 x1 和 x2 都不是 NaN 时，fmin 等价于 ``mt.where(x1 <= x2, x1, x2)``，但"
"它更快并且能正确广播。"

